data.description: Meticulously maintained, single-story Home in the desirable Ceniza Hills Subdivision. This charming 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom house is the perfect place to call home.   Its design is truly remarkable, features include an open kitchen, Stunning living area with high ceilings and Oversized windows for natural lighting. The eat in kitchen offers granite counter tops, cook-top and large island for eating & entertaining.  Master bedroom is a true retreat,  featuring a large walk-in closet with double vanities, and a walk-in shower. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this your new home. Schedule a viewing today!
